max_cor_clustering <- function(train_data, test_data, train_metadata, min_cor = 0, cluster_col = ) { # Compute cluster means unique_clusters <- unique(train_metadata[,cluster_col]) cluster_means <- do.call(rbind, lapply(unique_clusters, function(clust) { idx <- which(train_metadata[,cluster_col] == clust) exprs <- colMeans(train_data[idx,]) return(exprs) })) rownames(cluster_means) <- unique_clusters

# Map each cell to its max cor cluster cors <- cor(t(test_data), t(cluster_means)) mapped_groups <- apply(cors, 1, function(x) ifelse(max(x) >= min_cor, colnames(cors)[which.max(x)], NA))

return(mapped_groups) }

mapped_clusters <- max_cor_clustering(train_data, test_data, train_metadata, min_cor = 0, cluster_col = )

sim_test$cluster <- mapped_clusters

rr plotTSNE(sim_test, colour_by = )
